OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFarms look to the sky to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbeat soaring energy bills  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A solar power firm has reported record 
OL,6, demand from farms as the price of      
OL,7, electricity has risen.                 
OL,9,FMyPower, based in the Cotswolds, has   
OL,10,Finstalled 27,000 panels in the past    
OL,11,Fyear, up from 7,000 in the previous 12 
OL,12,Fmonths.                                
OL,14,FIts managing director Ben Harrison said
OL,15,Fhe believed energy price increases were
OL,16,Fbehind the dramatic sales growth.      
OL,18,F"Farms are facing rising electricity   
OL,19,Fbills, and making your own power can   
OL,20,Fhelp reduce that impact," he said.     
